(If you're sending the same email to everyone on your list, you're leaving money on the table. Here's the reality: a customer who spent $500 last month doesn't need the same message as someone who just signed up for your free trial. Segmentation—dividing your list into smaller groups—is how you make every email feel personal and relevant.) Tj
ET
